Walk the entire row and pick up every beeper, but be careful — not all positions have beepers! Use `if` to check before picking up.

Your solution must work for any arrangement of beepers. Use the dropdown to test different configurations.

> **Hint:** Don't forget to check Karel's starting position. The loop condition `front_is_clear()` only controls moving — you need to check for beepers separately.

